Date: Mon, 23 Jun 2025 00:21:26 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK: CP: wifi: ath12k Add BTWT and RTWT support in test cmds

BTWT and RTWT add extra params in add and delete dialog. FW added BTWT
invite sta and remove sta test commands. Add support of these new
commands and params.
echo "<MAC address <dialog_id>" >
/sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/netdev:wlan0/link0/twt/btwt_invite_sta
echo "<MAC address <dialog_id>" >
/sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/netdev:wlan0/link0/twt/btwt_remove_sta
